                                    Services (Sewage Charge) Regulation</docTitle><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">(<ref href="/hk/cap463/s12">Cap.
                                                463,
                                                section 12</ref> and <ref href="/hk/cap1/s29">Cap.
                                                1, section
                                    29</ref>)</enactingFormula><sourceNote>(Enacting provision omitted—<ref href="hk/2020/er2">E.R. 2 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote><commencementNote>[1 April 1995]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="hk/2020/er2">E.R. 2 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438403220321_002" name="s1" reason="omittedAsSpent" startPeriod="2020-03-26" status="omitted" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><sourceNote>(Omitted as spent—<ref href="hk/2020/er2">E.R. 2 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403220321_004" name="s2" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2020-03-26" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Sewage charges</heading><subsection id="ID_1438412577105_011" name="1" temporalId="s2_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><leadIn>Subject to subsection (2), for the purposes of <ref>section 3(1)</ref> of the
                Ordinance, the prescribed rate for each cubic metre of water (other than water
                supplied specifically for flushing purposes) supplied during a billing
                    period—<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2007/ln45">L.N. 45 of
                2007</ref>)</sourceNote></leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412577105_019" name="a" temporalId="s2_1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>that commences in a period specified in column 2 of <ref>Part 1 of Schedule
                        1</ref> shall be the rate specified in column 3 of <ref>Part 1 of Schedule
                        1</ref> opposite to that period;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412577105_027" name="b" temporalId="s2_1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>that commences on or after 1 April 2018 shall be the rate specified in
                        <ref>Part 2 of Schedule 1</ref>.<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2007/ln96">L.N. 96 of
                        2007</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412577121_005" name="2" temporalId="s2_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>For a trade, business or manufacture listed in <ref>Schedule 2</ref>, the amount charged under <ref>section 3(1)</ref> of the Ordinance shall be equal to 70% of the volume of water supplied, other than water supplied specifically for flushing purposes, multiplied by the rate prescribed under this section.<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1995/ln143">L.N. 143 of 1995</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subsection><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2007/ln45">L.N. 45 of 2007</ref>)</sourceNote><editorialNote type="footnote" id="ID_1578298731131_001"><content>Editorial Note:</content><leadIn>The amount of sewage charge payable pursuant to this section shall be reduced in respect of—</leadIn><subsection id="ID_1438412577121_047" name="a" temporalId="s2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>the period commencing on 1 April 2002 and ending on 31 March 2003 (please
                    see <ref>sections 2(2)</ref> and <ref>5</ref> of the Revenue (Variation and
                    Reduction of Fees and Charges) Order 2002 (<ref href="/hk/cap2R">Cap. 2 sub.
                        leg.
                    R</ref>));</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412577121_055" name="b" temporalId="s2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>bills scheduled to be issued within the period commencing on 1 August 2003
                    and ending on 30 November 2003 (please see <ref>sections 1 to 3</ref> of
                    the Sewage
                    Services (Reduction of Sewage Charge and Trade Effluent Surcharge) Regulation
                    2003 (<ref href="/hk/2003/ln131">L.N. 131 of
                    2003</ref>)).</content></subsection></editorialNote></section><section id="ID_1588144544762_001" name="s2A" temporalId="s2A" startPeriod="2022-12-01" status="operational" reason="inEffect"><num value="2A">2A.</num><heading>Sewage charge concessions for fresh water supplied for several non-domestic
            purposes between December 2019 and
            July
            2023</heading><sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln179">L.N. 179 of 2020</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/ln36">L.N.
                36 of 2021</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/ln188">L.N. 188 of
            2021</ref>; <ref href="hk/2022/ln29">L.N. 29 of
            2022</ref>; <ref href="hk/2022/ln223">L.N. 223 of 2022</ref>)</sourceNote><subsection id="ID_1588730734523_001" name="1" temporalId="s2A_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>This section applies in relation to the sewage charge for fresh water supplied
                during the concession period for use for a purpose described in item
                <ref>1(a)</ref>, (d), (e) or (f) of <ref>Part 3 of Schedule 1</ref> to the
                Waterworks Regulations (<ref href="/hk/cap102A">Cap. 102 sub. leg. A</ref>)
                    (<term>specified sewage charge</term>).</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1588730734523_002" name="2" temporalId="s2A_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>Despite <ref>section 2</ref> and subject to subsection (3), the amount of
                specified sewage charge is reduced by 75%.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1588730734523_003" name="3" temporalId="s2A_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><leadIn>
                <content>The amount that may be reduced under subsection (2) in relation to each
                    meter covered by a water bill must not exceed the maximum amount calculated in
                    accordance with the following formula—</content>
            </leadIn><continued>
                <table xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" width="100%">
                    <colgroup>
                        <col width="48%"></col>
                        <col width="6%"></col>
                        <col width="46%"></col>
                    </colgroup>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="align_left valign_center">
                                <p>maximum amount = $411.05</p>
                            </td>
                            <td class="align_left valign_center">
                                <p class="left_indent_2">×</p>
                            </td>
                            <td class="align_left">
                                <p class="align_justified">number of days that are covered by the
                                    water bill and that fall within the concession period.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </continued></subsection><subsection id="ID_1588730734523_004" name="4" temporalId="s2A_4"><num value="4">(4)</num><leadIn>If—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1588730734523_005" name="a" temporalId="s2A_4_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>the Water Authority issued, on a day before 29 April 2020 (<term>billing
                        day</term>), a water bill that covered the concession period (or a part of
                    it);</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1588730734523_006" name="b" temporalId="s2A_4_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>the amount of specified sewage charge (or a part of it) demanded in the
                    bill has been paid (whether before, on or after 29 April 2020); and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1588730734523_007" name="c" temporalId="s2A_4_c"><num value="c">(c)</num><content>the amount so paid is in excess of the amount of specified sewage charge
                    that should have been charged had this section been in force on the billing
                    day,</content></paragraph><continued>the Drainage Authority must refund the excess payment. <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln179">L.N. 179 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></continued></subsection><subsection id="ID_1588730734523_008" name="5" temporalId="s2A_5"><num value="5">(5)</num><leadIn>In this section—</leadIn><def name="ConcessionPeriod"><term>concession period</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">寬免期</term>) means the period from 1 December 2019 to
                31
                July 2023 (both dates inclusive); <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln179">L.N. 179 of 2020</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/ln36">L.N.
                        36 of 2021</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/ln188">L.N. 188 of
                    2021</ref>; <ref href="hk/2022/ln29">L.N. 29 of
                    2022</ref>; <ref href="hk/2022/ln223">L.N. 223 of
                    2022</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="Meter"><term>meter</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">水錶</term>) has the
                meaning given by <ref href="/hk/cap102/s2">section 2</ref> of the Waterworks
                Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap102">Cap. 102</ref>);</def><def name="WaterBill"><term>water bill</term> (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">水費單</term>)
                means a water bill issued by the Water Authority for a sewage charge.</def></subsection><sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln53">L.N. 53 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403220337_002" name="s3" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2020-03-26" status="operational" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><heading>Reduction of sewage charge by Drainage Authority</heading><content>For the purposes of <ref>section 9(1)(d)</ref> of the Ordinance, no sewage charge shall be reduced, waived or refunded unless the volume of wastewater being discharged into a communal drain or communal sewer is not more than 85% of the volume of water on which the sewage charge is based.</content></section><section id="ID_1438403220352_001" name="s4" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2007-07-01" status="repealed" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="/hk/2007/ln45">L.N. 45 of 2007</ref>)</sourceNote></section><schedule id="ID_1438403220352_003" name="sch1" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2020-03-26" status="operational" temporalId="sch1"><num value="1">Schedule
